<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Event Confirmation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      color: #333;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #1f90d1;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 0;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      margin-top: 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #888;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #1f90d1;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .footer a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .event-details {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
    .event-details ul {
      list-style-type: disc;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
    .button-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .confirm-button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #1f90d1;
      color: #fff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: bold;
      border-radius: 6px;
    }
    .confirm-button:hover {
      background-color: #166fa1;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Event Confirmation</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear <strong>{{guestName}}</strong>,</p>
      <p>Thank you for confirming your attendance. Weâ€™re excited to have you join us for <strong>{{eventName}}</strong>.</p>
      
      <div class="event-details">
        <h3>Event Details</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Date:</strong> {{eventDate}}</li>
          <li><strong>Time:</strong> {{eventTime}}</li>
          <li><strong>Venue:</strong> {{eventVenue}}</li>
         
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p>Please keep this email as your confirmation. A reminder will be sent one day before the event.</p>
      <p>We look forward to welcoming you.</p>

      <!-- New text and button -->
      <p>If you would like to edit or update your details or add additional guest names, please click the Edit button below.</p>
      <div class="button-container">
        <a href="https://tigerinvites.com/edit?id={{id}}" class="confirm-button">Edit</a>
      </div>

      <p>Best regards,<br><strong>{{organizerName}}</strong></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
